      "evidence_quote": "In the short story \"The Borrowed Name,\" Jordan adopts a fake identity online to feel safer and more confident.",
      "rationale": "Shows knowledge of the chosen text, but does not demonstrate subject-specific content knowledge tied to the assigned novel (*Ghost*), and includes no author/page citation details expected in the assignment."
    },
    {
      "criterion_id": "K2",
      "level": "3",
      "score": 75,
      "evidence_quote": "the author suggests that hiding who you are may seem protective, but it often produces consequences like anxiety, mistrust, and isolation.",
      "rationale": "Demonstrates a clear, accurate understanding of the theme and cause-effect relationship (hiding identity → emotional/social consequences) with consistent interpretation across paragraphs."
    },
    {
      "criterion_id": "T1",
      "level": "3",
